as's doubts have made him seem a very human character."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Thomas de Culwen of Workington was born about 1110, in High Ireby, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom, his father, Thomas de Culwen I, was 22 and his mother, unknown, was 19. He had at least 1 daughter with Margaret. He died on 7 December 1152, in Workington, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 43."},"et":{"Abt 1110–7 December 1152":"umbes 1110–7. detsember 1152","1110–1152":"1110–1152","1115–Female":"1115–Surnud","1135–1201":"1135–1201","1089–Male":"1089–Surnud","1093–Female":"1093–Surnud","1115":"1115","1135":"1135","1201":"1201","7 December 1152":"7. detsember 1152","Abt 1110":"umbes 1110","1089":"1089","1110":"1110","1152":"1152","1093":"1093","High Ireby, Embleton, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom":"High Ireby, Cumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Workington Hall, Workington, Cumberland, England":"Workington, Cumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1110–7 December 1152":"noin 1110–7. joulukuuta 1152","1110–1152":"1110–1152","1115–Female":"1115–Kuollut","1135–1201":"1135–1201","1089–Male":"1089–Kuollut","1093–Female":"1093–Kuollut","1115":"1115","1135":"1135","1201":"1201","7 December 1152":"7. joulukuuta 1152","Abt 1110":"noin 1110","1089":"1089","1110":"1110","1152":"1152","1093":"1093","High Ireby, Embleton, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom":"High Ireby, Cumberland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Workington Hall, Workington, Cumberland, England":"Workington, Cumberland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1110–7 December 1152":"environ 1110–7 décembre 1152","1110–1152":"1110–1152","1115–Female":"1115–Décédée","1135–1201":"1135–1201","1089–Male":"1089–Décédé","1093–Female":"1093–Décédée","1115":"1115","1135":"1135","1201":"1201","7 December 1152":"7 décembre 1152","Abt 1110":"environ 1110","1089":"1089","1110":"1110","1152":"1152","1093":"1093","High Ireby, Embleton, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom":"High Ireby,